OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTrudeau says monarchy      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Foffers Canada 'steadiness' 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Prime Minister Justin Trudeau said he  
OL,6, doesn't see Canada breaking ties with  
OL,7, the British Crown anytime soon.        
OL,9,FThe complexities of moving away from a 
OL,10,Fconstitutional monarchy are not what   
OL,11,F"Canadians are overly taken up with    
OL,12,Fright now", he told the BBC.           
OL,14,FHe said he appreciated the "steadiness"
OL,15,Fof the current system.                 
OL,17,FMr Trudeau is also facing controversy  
OL,18,Fafter a video captured him singing a   
OL,19,Fsong by British rock band Queen in a   
OL,20,FLondon hotel over the weekend.         
